\begin{verse}
kaM|| irutiha gaCaCxdoLoMdanu | sarigaLiduLidaSuTxGAta guNakoVtatxrava|| naritu mADutatx ladariM | dharinaMtayxda baMdalabadhx vAdipadakukxM||

vi|| guNoVtatxra saMKayxvanunx gaCaCxdalilx oMdu kaDameyAdaSuTx GAtavanunx mADi, adariMda aMtayx padavanunx BAgisidare baruva labadhxveV Adi padavAgiruvadu.
\end{verse}

udAharaNe, guNoVtatxra $2$, gaCaCx $20$, aMtayxpada $524288$ idadxre Adi padaveSuTx?

\qq\qq $\dfrac{524288}{20-1}=\dfrac{524288}{524288}=1$ idu Adi padavu.

\begin{center}
{\bf\large 111neV aBayx udAharaNe.}
\end{center}

\begin{enumerate}[\rm (1)]
\item guNoVtatxravu $\tfrac{1}{2},\tfrac{1}{4} 4,$ gaCaCxvu $24, 10, 12,$ aMtayxpadavu $\tfrac{1}{16777216}, \tfrac{1}{1048576}, 12582912$ Adare AdipadagaLeSuTx?

\item obabx garxhasathxnu $16$ divasagaLa varige parxti divasavU nAlukx nAlakxraSuTx hecucx hecAcxgi dharamxvanunx mADalAgi $22369621$ rUpAyi $5$ ANe $4$ peY vecacxvAyitu. Agalu modalaneV divasa eSuTxkoTaTxnu heVLu?
\end{enumerate}
